query:
INSERT INTO notification
                  (
                    id,
                    title,
                    status,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    last_read_at,
                    snoozed_until,
                    user_id,
                    task_id,
                    kind,
                    source_item_id
                  )
                VALUES
                  ($1, $2, $3::notification_status, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10::notification_source_kind, $11)
                RETURNING
                  id
